import {
  Box,
  Button,
  Center,
  Flex,
  Heading,
  Image,
  Spacer,
  Text,
} from "@chakra-ui/react";
import React from "react";

const Home = () => {
  return (
    <Box id="home" p={10}>
      <Box
        w="90%"
        h="100%"
        display="flex"
        justifyContent="space-evenly"
        alignItems="center"
      >
        <Box>
          <Heading>
            {" "}
            Hey ! I'm
            <Heading id="user-detail-name"> Shivam</Heading>
          </Heading>
          <Text id="user-detail-intro">Full stack web Developer</Text>
          <Button>CONTACT ME</Button>
          <Button>RESUME</Button>
        </Box>
        <Box>
          <Image
            borderRadius="full"
            boxSize="300px"
            src="https://bit.ly/dan-abramov"
            alt="Dan Abramov"
          />
        </Box>
      </Box>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Home;
